{"tid":2268764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電訊公司技術員向老豆搵仔爆料囚兩年 為首宗經審訊後定罪起底案件","createTime":"2020-11-03T05:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T07:18:27.000Z","uid":310914,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc31500bd2c1b6a233e97d23cce3930f7308b6cd","tid":2268764,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"香港電訊（HKT）男技術員涉擅自登入公司電腦，搜尋及擷取警員家屬資料，再向Telegram「老豆搵仔」頻道發佈。技術員早前在區域法院經審訊後，被裁定不誠實取用電腦等四項罪名成立。法官姚勳智今判刑時指社會事件令警民關係變得緊張，警員家屬資料被發佈至網上，對執法者構成嚴重心理影響，亦對無辜家屬造成極大心理困擾，明言難以接納被告求情稱只因一時衝動才犯案的說法，故須判處阻嚇性刑罰，判監兩年。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">其他嗰啲自己俾錢睇</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/TZLUFWIQRRCUZN56LIBOVEQA5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FTZLUFWIQRRCUZN56LIBOVEQA5M%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0ErXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=f956c5a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FTZLUFWIQRRCUZN56LIBOVEQA5M%2F&h=058641c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/TZLUFWIQRRCUZN56LIBOVEQA5M/</a>"},{"pid":"a3c87694076f55e2b4942e0ac5ab190f9817f9b7","tid":2268764,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2b34df84650a1e467d174a16d1de19a57e9be4","tid":2268764,"uid":32148,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:24:56.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法治已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.g